Next time you find yourself in Seoul, take the opportunity to explore the innovative treatments in Gangnam. From the icy immersion of cryotherapy to the serene floatation tanks, you’ll discover new ways to rejuvenate your body and mind, leaving you feeling refreshed and revitalized.

